title: Should we add JUV and PSG Syrup Pools?
body:
## Stake CAKE tokens, to earn JUV tokens!
**Total Tokens:** 20,000 JUV (Currently worth over $300,000!)
**Distribution duration:** 30 days
**Reward Start block:** 3285150 (Dec 21st 3pm)
**Reward End bock:** 4149150 (Jan 20th 3pm)
**JUV reward per block:** 0.023148 JUV


## Stake CAKE tokens, to earn PSG tokens!
**Total Tokens:** 20,000 PSG (Currently worth over $280,000!)
**Distribution duration:**30 days
**Reward Start block:** 3285150 (Dec 21st 3pm)
**Reward End bock:** 4149150 (Jan 20th 3pm)
**PSG reward per block:** 0.023148 PSG


In order to host the JUV and PSG Syrup Pools, we will need to provide them with a farm each. Both farms will have BNB pairs (JUV-BNB, PSG-BNB) and 1x CAKE rewards.

Why do we need a vote? Since it dilutes rewards, the chefs want BSC's greatest community to make the decision themselves.
